name: Turquoise Vocho- Vocho Lindo y Querido #7
description:
The series “Vocho Lindo y Querido: a love story from 1967 to 2003” explores a cultural icon, the “Vocho” –or Volkswagen Beetle–, in the context of Mexicanness over the last five decades, through 36 NFTs on the Tezos Blockchain, one for each year the car was produced in the plant of Puebla, Mexico. For more information, visit: https://natalielarrode.com/vocho-lindo-y-querido/

Mix of digital processes: drawing, photography, and illustration.

4096px X 4096px png by @natlarrode.

* This image has been printed in a limited edition of 10 signed and numbered copies.
